::Aerotaur::
       He looks up after hearing the shot.  He shakes his head.  "I've got to 
go, the new base will have to wait."  He runs up to the bridge.  He looks 
around and dashes to the defense panel, he raises the shields and activates 
the autocannons.  They open fire on Virgo, Lee, Barrymore, Birdbot, and 
Papertron.

--part1_197.f878bf.2971bccb_boundary
